com.objetdirect.tatami.client
Class DateUtil

java.lang.Object
  com.objetdirect.tatami.client.DateUtil

public class DateUtil
extends java.lang.Object

Group of utilitarian methods of manipulation / edition of dates. These methods integrate some DOJO functions. They allow of landing the fact that GWT does'nt integrate DateFormat in the JRE emulation library. TODO : add some usefull methods from DOJO 0.9

Author:
Henry,Vianney
